      "widgets_values": [
        "### Workflow order\n1. Leave `existing_group_id` empty in `SeedanceCreateHumanAsset`\n2. Queue only that node first\n3. Complete **Start Verification** inside the node\n4. Queue the same node again to get the final `asset_id`\n5. Save the `group_id`\n6. Then queue `Seedance2` to generate the video\n\n### Important\n- The verification button/link appears in `SeedanceCreateHumanAsset`\n- `SeedanceShowText` is only for reading `asset_id` and `group_id`\n- Real-human verification works with `AnyFast`, not `fal.ai`\n- For preview, use your preferred common video loader/preview node after generation"
